{"title":"安装PicGo中的picgo-plugin-compress插件","slug":"安装PicGo中的picgo-plugin-compress插件","date":"2021-12-17T15:33:34.000Z","updated":"2024-07-11T08:16:34.957Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/安装PicGo中的picgo-plugin-compress插件.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217233444390.webp","/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217234115720.webp","/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217234439905.webp"],"content":"<p>下载PigGo</p>\n<p><img src=\"/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217233444390.webp\" alt=\"image-20211217233444390\"></p>\n<p>在PigGo的更目录执行下面命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install picgo-plugin-compress --save --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如果报错下面信息那就这些这个命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npmmirror.com</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">cnpm install picgo-plugin-compress --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217234115720.webp\"></p>\n<p>然后在PicGo里面配置就好了，点击启用transformer-compress</p>\n<p><img src=\"/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217234439905.webp\" alt=\"image-20211217234439905\"></p>\n","more":"<p>下载PigGo</p>\n<p><img src=\"/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217233444390.webp\" alt=\"image-20211217233444390\"></p>\n<p>在PigGo的更目录执行下面命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install picgo-plugin-compress --save --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如果报错下面信息那就这些这个命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npmmirror.com</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">cnpm install picgo-plugin-compress --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217234115720.webp\"></p>\n<p>然后在PicGo里面配置就好了，点击启用transformer-compress</p>\n<p><img src=\"/posts/4c3fd5bc/image-20211217234439905.webp\" alt=\"image-20211217234439905\"></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}